window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ring! Ring! Ring! Are those wedding bells, or the toll of the grave?</b></p> <p>I never expected I’d become a mighty wizard, let alone a married man with five wonderful brides, but it seems things have been working out in my favor. My lair is expanding, new opportunities abound, and I’ve been taking lessons from some of the most powerful hearthomancers to have ever lived.</p> <p>But that dang noise keeps ringing in my ears. Where is it coming from? And how is a phantom from my past, long since thought defeated, now threatening not just my life, but the lives of everyone I know and care about?</p> <p>Threats arise as the wedding ceremony draws closer. Enemies stand before my gates, ready to steal everything I own.</p> <p><b>I will defend my home and ensure my lovers and I earn the happily ever after we fought so hard for.</b></p>"; 
